<b>Figure 6:</b> (Left) Elastic modulus (\(E_e/E_1\)), and (Right) strain hardening rate (\(E_p/E_1\)) with the volume fraction, for microstructures with randomly distributed inclusions (open symbols) and fractal microstructures (various filled symbols). \(E_1\) represents the matrix modulus.
