    </div>
</div>
<figcaption>
<b>Figure 7:</b> (Left) Vitrimer stress relaxation at various temperatures. (Right) Arrhenius plot of the relaxation time constant against the inverse temperature showing two regimes: the straight line, Arrhenius dependence on temperature (right side of the plot) and the transition at \(T_v\) to a quasi-plateau (left side of the plot). 
